These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, baccarat, dunhill, fonseca, tiparillo, oliveros
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is the argentine##1
 8. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Cigar           | fonseca | dunhill | alhambra | baccarat | bongani | tiparillo | oliveros |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

