.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, june, january, may, april, february, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Birthday   | june      | january   | may   | april      | july       | october       | february     |

