.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
City: boston, hamburg, berlin, venice, miami, san-francisco, london
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is the person eating onion##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| City    | san-francisco  | boston | london | venice | hamburg | berlin | miami |

