.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, surfing, climbing, sailing, volleyball, basketball
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is the australian##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the thai is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Sport   | volleyball    | basketball     | climbing     | surfing      | ice-hockey | sailing      | swimming     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

