There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, milk, cola, juice, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Beverage     | iced-tea   | milk    | juice | hot-chocolate     | lemonade         | cola     | mirinda        |

