.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, biathlon, weightlifting, baseball, basketball, handball
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Sport    | biathlon | basketball   | volleyball | weightlifting | handball  | baseball | soccer |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

