 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the fan of indie##1
 8. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of soul##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | soul | country | pop | trance     | salsa | indie |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

