.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
7 different games are played: chess, domino, backgammon, go, bridge, scrabble, whist
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing go is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person playing bridge is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing domino##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| Game   | scrabble | go  | whist    | chess | bridge | domino       | backgammon   |

